ets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新界撚表示冇乜點聽過身邊嘅人屋企係用淡水冲廁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T15:09:37.000Z","msg":"村屋撚一定要淡水沖<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/mask.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3935dc1eec030cf142f3ff9de47fa0570333a7f","tid":2222950,"uid":1333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa95a0fbd6b71baff9d653d324823287aef6f59c","tid":2222950,"uid":18521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"887bb3d715dbe80e9d8d86331194a25b9f257c00","tid":2222950,"uid":67257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"769969f8e8747bb318d5deb4bed576d3d6e5ad83","tid":2222950,"uid":18521,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:08:45.000Z","msg":"得新界用淡水沖廁"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新界撚表示冇乜點聽過身邊嘅人屋企係用淡水冲廁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:20:52.000Z","msg":"2013年7月31日，香港有兩成人口，即130多萬人口使用淡水沖廁[72]，地區包括南區、山頂、西貢、北區（粉嶺、上水）、元朗、屯門東及離島區[73]，2015年，水務署成功延伸沖廁海水管網，新界西北（包括屯門東、洪水橋、天水圍和元朗市中心等）及薄扶林區內的樓宇已可轉用海水沖廁，並計劃把海水供應網絡擴展至東涌[63]。而港島山頂、南區、西貢及離島區人口比較分散，所以並無制定海水沖廁的計劃。而北區未獲提供海水沖廁，是因為人口比較密集的上水和粉嶺區不貼近任何海岸[73]。<br />\n<br />\n淡水沖廁年耗8200萬立方米淡水[74]。住宅使用之沖廁淡水由政府補貼，一年花去超過三億公帑[75]。水務處現正開始擴建於薄扶林、元朗及天水圍沖廁用的海水供應系統；新界西北的海水沖廁水系統已於2015年初完工[76]，獲供海水沖廁的人口提升至八成半[72]，東涌海水供應系統的規劃工作亦已展開[77]。而上水和粉嶺區則研究使用再造水沖廁[78]。<br />\n- <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%25B0%25B4&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=eb9a7610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4</a><br />\n<br />\n新界西北及薄扶林新增海水沖廁<br />\n<br />\n除了屯門東區，水務署亦將海水供應網絡擴展至洪水橋、天水圍、元朗市中心及薄扶林等地區，令本港海水覆蓋率增至八成半人口。當新增覆蓋地區的海水供應網絡全面實施後，每年亦可節省約2,000萬立方米食水量。<br />\n- Nov, 2018<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/262778/%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%85%B3%E6%B0%B4%E8%B2%BB-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%9D%B1%E9%A3%9F%E6%B0%B4%E6%B2%96%E5%BB%81%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E8%AE%8A%E9%B9%B9%E6%B0%B4-%E9%A6%96%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E9%81%B8%E5%AE%9A29%E5%80%8B%E5%9C%B0%E9%BB%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F262778%2F%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2585%25B3%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%25B2%25BB-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%259D%25B1%25E9%25A3%259F%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25B2%2596%25E5%25BB%2581%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%259B%25E8%25AE%258A%25E9%25B9%25B9%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%259A%258E%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25AE%259A29%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%25BB%259E&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=6de9ccff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/262778/%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%85%B3%E6%B0%B4%E8%B2%BB-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%9D%B1%E9%A3%9F%E6%B0%B4%E6%B2%96%E5%BB%81%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E8%AE%8A%E9%B9%B9%E6%B0%B4-%E9%A6%96%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E9%81%B8%E5%AE%9A29%E5%80%8B%E5%9C%B0%E9%BB%9E</a><br />\n<br />\n當2018已經減少2000萬，即係近兩年仲有大約6000萬立方米水拎來沖廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T15:20:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20170423/WJOF5Y4AQT7BRJGWQ3PYQW655A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20170423%2FWJOF5Y4AQT7BRJGWQ3PYQW655A%2F&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=f03949e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20170423%2FWJOF5Y4AQT7BRJGWQ3PYQW655A%2F&h=b2cb30a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20170423/WJOF5Y4AQT7BRJGWQ3PYQW655A/</a><br />\n<br />\n東江水年年用剩<br />\n議員轟浪費50億<br />\n更新時間 (HKT): 2017.04.23 05:20<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢頭倒淡水落海<br />\n再將海水抽返上黎沖廁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afd8c402195ab9c1c33824bdca39d800ea397a4","tid":2222950,"uid":289900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8413115de695757d3d5c88c7b19bb766168d41b6","tid":2222950,"uid":33851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"887bb3d715dbe80e9d8d86331194a25b9f257c00","tid":2222950,"uid":67257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"769969f8e8747bb318d5deb4bed576d3d6e5ad83","tid":2222950,"uid":18521,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:08:45.000Z","msg":"得新界用淡水沖廁"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新界撚表示冇乜點聽過身邊嘅人屋企係用淡水冲廁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.wsd.gov.hk/filemanager/tc/content_1880/Supply-zone.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsd.gov.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Ftc%2Fcontent_1880%2FSupply-zone.jpg&h=9a7ff0fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"睇落好似新界好多人都冇鹹水沖廁<br />\n實際上新界絕大部份人口都住喺新市鎮範圍<br />\n其餘地區都係山旮旯冇乜人住<br />\n<br />\n目前9個新市鎮：<br />\n荃灣新市鎮：有鹹水沖廁<br />\n沙田新市鎮：有鹹水沖廁<br />\n屯門新市鎮：有鹹水沖廁<br />\n大埔新市鎮：有鹹水沖廁<br />\n元朗新市鎮：有鹹水沖廁<br />\n粉嶺/上水新市鎮：冇<br />\n將軍澳新市鎮：有鹹水沖廁<br />\n天水圍新市鎮：有鹹水沖廁<br />\n東涌新市鎮：興建中<br />\n<br />\n即係得粉嶺/上水新市鎮冇+東涌起緊未起完+得零丁人口既山旮旯冇<br />\n睇地圖睇落好似好多地方都冇鹹水沖廁<br />\n實際上新界絕大部份人口都有"},{"pid":"74e06defc916b851cc334c49f274ef7ea95f1b15","tid":2222950,"uid":69898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"用少咗東江水唔等於買少啲東江水<br />\n年年都有剩嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從來都係政治問題黎"}],"pinned":{"pid":"aa95a0fbd6b71baff9d653d324823287aef6f59c","tid":2222950,"uid":18521,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T14:20:52.000Z","msg":"2013年7月31日，香港有兩成人口，即130多萬人口使用淡水沖廁[72]，地區包括南區、山頂、西貢、北區（粉嶺、上水）、元朗、屯門東及離島區[73]，2015年，水務署成功延伸沖廁海水管網，新界西北（包括屯門東、洪水橋、天水圍和元朗市中心等）及薄扶林區內的樓宇已可轉用海水沖廁，並計劃把海水供應網絡擴展至東涌[63]。而港島山頂、南區、西貢及離島區人口比較分散，所以並無制定海水沖廁的計劃。而北區未獲提供海水沖廁，是因為人口比較密集的上水和粉嶺區不貼近任何海岸[73]。<br />\n<br />\n淡水沖廁年耗8200萬立方米淡水[74]。住宅使用之沖廁淡水由政府補貼，一年花去超過三億公帑[75]。水務處現正開始擴建於薄扶林、元朗及天水圍沖廁用的海水供應系統；新界西北的海水沖廁水系統已於2015年初完工[76]，獲供海水沖廁的人口提升至八成半[72]，東涌海水供應系統的規劃工作亦已展開[77]。而上水和粉嶺區則研究使用再造水沖廁[78]。<br />\n- <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BE%259B%25E6%25B0%25B4&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=eb9a7610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BE%9B%E6%B0%B4</a><br />\n<br />\n新界西北及薄扶林新增海水沖廁<br />\n<br />\n除了屯門東區，水務署亦將海水供應網絡擴展至洪水橋、天水圍、元朗市中心及薄扶林等地區，令本港海水覆蓋率增至八成半人口。當新增覆蓋地區的海水供應網絡全面實施後，每年亦可節省約2,000萬立方米食水量。<br />\n- Nov, 2018<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/262778/%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%85%B3%E6%B0%B4%E8%B2%BB-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%9D%B1%E9%A3%9F%E6%B0%B4%E6%B2%96%E5%BB%81%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E8%AE%8A%E9%B9%B9%E6%B0%B4-%E9%A6%96%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E9%81%B8%E5%AE%9A29%E5%80%8B%E5%9C%B0%E9%BB%9E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F18%25E5%258D%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F262778%2F%25E5%258F%25AF%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E6%2585%25B3%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E8%25B2%25BB-%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%259D%25B1%25E9%25A3%259F%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%25B2%2596%25E5%25BB%2581%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%259B%25E8%25AE%258A%25E9%25B9%25B9%25E6%25B0%25B4-%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%259A%258E%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25AE%259A29%25E5%2580%258B%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%25BB%259E&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXB9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=6de9ccff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/18%E5%8D%80%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/262778/%E5%8F%AF%E4%BB%A5%E6%85%B3%E6%B0%B4%E8%B2%BB-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%9D%B1%E9%A3%9F%E6%B0%B4%E6%B2%96%E5%BB%81%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E8%AE%8A%E9%B9%B9%E6%B0%B4-%E9%A6%96%E9%9A%8E%E6%AE%B5%E9%81%B8%E5%AE%9A29%E5%80%8B%E5%9C%B0%E9%BB%9E</a><br />\n<br />\n當2018已經減少2000萬，即係近兩年仲有大約6000萬立方米水拎來沖廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}